<h3>Vasectomy Consent and Agreement:</h3><div class="vasectomy-consent" style="font-size: small; font-style: italic; line-height: 1;">
    <p>
      Before proceeding with the vasectomy, please review and consent to the following:
    </p>
    <ul style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
      <li>You have read the information provided on our website regarding no-scalpel no-needle vasectomy.</li>
      <li>If you have a history of fainting, it's advised to bring a driver with you for the procedure.</li>
      <li>Refrain from alcohol consumption 24 hours before and after the procedure.</li>
      <li>Avoid taking aspirin, anticoagulants (warfarin), or anti-inflammatories (NSAIDs) such as ibuprofen, Advil, Motrin, Aleve, etc., for 7 days before and after the operation.</li>
      <li>Have a discussion with your partner about the decision to undergo a vasectomy, and ensure they are supportive of your choice. Feel free to contact our office to discuss further if needed.</li>
      <li>Be aware that failure to follow pre-procedure instructions or cancellation with short notice may incur a $200 cancellation fee.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="vasectomy-consent-agreement" style="display: block; font-size: small; font-style: italic;">
        <input type="checkbox" name="vasectomy-consent-agreement" required>I have read and consent to the Vasectomy Consent and Agreement.
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>


